Changes in version 1.0.4 (February 8, 2015):

  * Make CITATION readable without having the package installed.

Changes in version 1.0.3 (March 3, 2013):

  * Fixed a bug trying to read in numbers with more than 15 digits.

Changes in version 1.0.2 (September 28, 2012):

  * Added the github URL of the package.
  * Using full names in the Author and Maintainer fields.

Changes in version 1.0.1 (April 21, 2012):

